 Low temp {{{lowTemp}}} at 
 {{{lowTempTime}}}.
 High temp {{{highTemp}}} at
 {{{highTempTime}}}.
 Wind: {{{windDirection}}} at {{{windSpeed}}} mph.
 Sunrise: {{{sunriseTime}}}.
 Sunset: {{{sunsetTime}}}.
</p>
{{/daily_loop}}
</div>


